 to watch. Gameplay is butter smooth and there is no bug encountered just yet. Since this is the original, it goes without saying that the resolution could only be maxed to 1024x640 (16 or 32 bit) and not beyond. For newcomers such as myself, I recommend that you finished the remastered edition first to develop interest before playing the original. I would also like to express my gratitude for having this game included together by the developer as it kept me invested in the game and its a blast to play with.Pros:+ Epic Story and lore+ Great gameplay+ Has great valueCons:- None so far=============================================================================*MORE REVIEWS TO COME*"
