,Recommended,244160,14685753,"Posted: 27 February, 2015",all,appaloosa51,AWESOME USING NVIDIA ... I had the older Homeworld 2 ... the remastered is lots better ... however .. it is graphical intense really utilizing everythingy your Nvidia has ... but . it worth it as u will see if u get the game .. if u r uisng Nividia u could get also an error on first use ... it will lock and freeze ... do NOT worry ... no problem .... it is NOT the game nor your Nvidia card .. its in the settings .... the error will say OPEN GL HAS LOST CONNECTON WITH YOUR GRAPHICS CARD ... this is only for Nividia ... here is how to fix that ... the problem is .. it is looking for a time out to load the graphics ... as I said it is graphic intense but worth it ... to fix it ... all u do is on your main computer screen open the Nvidia Control Panel ... in the main Control Panel for GLOBAL ... if u look u will more than likely see that you have set yout GLOBAL SETTING OF POWER MANAGEMENT MODE to ADAPTIVE ... all u do is change your GLOBAL setting to PREFER MAXIMUM PERFORMANCE ... and wham bam ... all solved and u can play all u want .. what this does is open your Nvidia to use every resource it has for awesome graphics ... and believe me ... u will luv it .. if u do NOT set it to Perfer Max Performance u mite crash and burn ... I luv this game and give it awesome stars ! ... now go ... find your homeworld ... and have fun ... its totally Awesome ! ... GET IT TODAY ! ..
